These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: papaya, lemon, spinach
1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
2. the person eating papaya is on the far right##1
3. the person eating papaya is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Food   | spinach | lemon | papaya |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, may, july
1. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Birthday   | october | july | may |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, train, quad-bike
1. the person driving the train is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Transport   | bike | train | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
